oc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#first-of-type%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">first-of-type選擇器</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%A8-type-%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87-input\"><span class=\"toc-text\">用 type 選擇 input</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#opacity-%E4%BE%86%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%AD%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%81%BD%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E4%BE%86%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%E5%BC%8F%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">opacity 來預設消失元素，使用偽元素來條件式顯示</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8E%BB%E9%99%A4%E9%BB%9E%E9%81%B8%E7%9A%84%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%AD%E5%A4%96%E6%A1%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">去除點選的預設外框</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#JS-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">JS</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%B8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">設定變數</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E5%88%B0-list-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">新增資料到 list 上測試</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#init\"><span class=\"toc-text\">init()</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E7%B8%BD%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">設定總金額，支出，收入的元素</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#updateValues\"><span class=\"toc-text\">updateValues()</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#generateID\"><span class=\"toc-text\">generateID()</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E9%81%B8%E5%8F%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">刪除選取的代辦事項</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#submit-%E7%9B%A3%E8%81%BD%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">submit 監聽事件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A-Local-Storage-%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">設定 Local Storage 存取資料</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"(Project) LocalStorage ToDoList","uid":"3371b618f27c97a84db4478a4567e2f2","slug":"Localstorage_ ToDoList","date":"2021-02-23T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.458Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Localstorage_ ToDoList.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"Localstorage: ToDoListDemo說明專案概要 輸入內容 點擊加入待辦事項 下方依照順序列出待辦事項，並可以點擊刪除 &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;text&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;textClass&quot; pl...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":42,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"},{"name":"作品集","slug":"JavaScript/作品集","count":18,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript/作品集.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":36,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"},{"name":"作品集","slug":"作品集","count":19,"path":"api/tags/作品集.json"}],"author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"JavaScript LocalStorage","uid":"3ca09683192d71f47139468ac4ff2bd4","slug":"localstorage","date":"2021-02-21T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.556Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/localstorage.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"LocalStoragelocalStorage 是瀏覽器裡面的資料庫，比如說瀏覽商城的時候，會有欄位顯示瀏覽過的商品，這就是透過 localStorage 的方式紀錄下來的。要注意到，localStorage 儲存資料的方式是以 string 的方式，也就是字串。 在 chro...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.3k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":42,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":36,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}